### Create menu (admin)
POST http://localhost:4000/menu
Content-Type: application/json
Cookie: token=PASTE_TOKEN

{
  "day": "Monday",
  "items": [],
  "notes": "Weekly menu sample"
}

### Get full weekly menu
GET http://localhost:4000/menu

### Get menu by day
GET http://localhost:4000/menu/Monday

### Update menu
PUT http://localhost:4000/menu/PASTE_MENU_ID
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "notes": "Updated notes"
}

### Delete menu
DELETE http://localhost:4000/menu/PASTE_MENU_ID
